### Lesson 0009: create an item to update
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Patch Practice Item",
  "category": "tool",
  "price": 10,
  "in_stock": true
}

### Lesson 0009: partially update the item
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 12.5,
  "in_stock": false
}

### Lesson 0009: delete the item
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/4

